From a1e5ee8135fc19e38f540ccf658303a8ec5d68e6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
Date: Fri, 24 Apr 2026 23:20:29 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] feat: Add macOS 26 icon format, app bundle builder, and menu bar improvements

Add initial hacky version of macOS 26 icon format and basic app bundle builder, add version of notification bindings, add help menu and automatic hiding support for menu bar app, allow refocusing app if opened via bundle

Signed-off-by: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
---
